verbose_text: Interestingly, the most powerful secondary phenol donors on the imides raised the LUMO from PDI 21 to PDI 25 by DeltaE LUMO = +40 meV, whereas the same secondary phenols lowered the LUMO of the original NDI 1 to NDI 4 by DeltaE LUMO = -30 meV.
